description: This is the Transfer of Knowledge Through Expatriate Nationals, which was operationalized in 2006 to provide emergency capacity building support to the Government of Liberia (GOL) to implement its development and reform agenda.

subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: Capacity of Government of Liberia (GOL) ministries and agencies strengthened to carry out their assigned functions and in accordance with their mandates
subproject.gender code: No noticeable contribution to gender equality
